  <!-- ===== ADMISSION CONTENT ===== -->
  <section class="admission-container">
    <h2>Step-by-Step Admission Guide</h2>
    <p>
      Our admission process is designed to ensure fairness, transparency, and equal opportunity for all applicants.
      Below is the detailed procedure for securing admission into our institution.
    </p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step" data-step="1">
        <h3>Obtain Application Form</h3>
        <p>
          Application forms can be obtained from the Admission Office or downloaded online through the institution's
          official portal.
          Ensure you read the admission requirements before filling out the form.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="2">
        <h3>Complete the Application Form</h3>
        <p>
          Fill in your personal, academic, and contact information accurately. Attach all necessary documents, including
          your credentials,
          recent passport photograph, and payment receipt (if applicable).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="3">
        <h3>Submit the Form</h3>
        <p>
          Submit your completed form to the Admission Office or upload it online before the deadline.
          Late submissions may not be processed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="4">
        <h3>Screening and Interview</h3>
        <p>
          All applicants will undergo a screening exercise.
          Shortlisted candidates may also be invited for an interview or aptitude test as part of the selection process.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="5">
        <h3>Admission Notification</h3>
        <p>
          Successful candidates will receive an official admission letter via email or can check their status on the
          school’s admission portal.
          Proceed to accept your admission and begin registration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

